bop_clean_ts %>% 
  filter(date > "1970-01-01") %>% 
  group_by(development_flag) %>% 
  mutate(label = if_else(date == max(date), as.character(development_flag), NA_character_)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = date,
             y = balance_of_payments, colour = development_flag))+
  geom_vline(xintercept = as.numeric(bop_clean_ts$date[49]), linetype = 1, colour = "red")+
  annotate("text", x = bop_clean_ts$date[48], 
           y = 5, label = "2008 GFC", angle = 90, colour = "red")+
  geom_text_repel(aes(label = label, colour = development_flag),
                   na.rm = TRUE, 
                   check_overlap = TRUE)+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::comma)+
  geom_line(labels = scale)+
  theme_minimal()+
  theme(legend.position = "none")+
  labs(title = "UK Balance of Payments vs Developed Countries",
       y = "Balance of Payments ($)",
       x = "Date")
